 0px;\">\r\n	The image is very important if we enjoy the city. This department not only ensures that dailydeals have good presentation but to create a visual experience since the deals purchases until you enjoy with your friends.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Accounts</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	The Accounts department is concerned beyond dailydeals carry a simple business deals. Ensures that grow brands by offering new experiences to our members and affiliates.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Press</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	There is always something interesting to do and Press Department is in charge of making you get the best of reviewing topics such as food, travel, technology, art, fashion, health and trends, to name a few.</p>', '<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Dailydeals</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>offers daily deals for all tastes. From gastronomy, health and beauty to travel and escape. Our goal is to offer attractive options and quality to our members to enhance their experience in seeking a better lifestyle. We look for things that define a place as those to be discovered. Design experiences in your city to enjoy with your friends. Innovation and imagination have made dailydeals is the fastest growing company in the social category of purchase. dailydeals means living with a real connection. We shape life social.</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	Founders</h4>\r\n<div class=\"repeatCell\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<div class=\"photo\">\r\n		<img alt=\"Tim\" id=\"founder-img\" src=\"../images/team_1.jpg\" style=\"cursor: default;\" /></div>\r\n	<h5>\r\n		Tim O&#39;Shaughnessy<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span>CEO and Co-Founder</span></h5>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Tim sets and communicates BitFatDeals core strategy, and oversees our growth as the next great consumer brand. Before BitFatDeals, Tim led the consumer products team at Revolution Health and managed product launches at AOL. Tim graduated from Georgetown University with degrees in Marketing and Operations &amp; Information Management.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"repeatCell\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<div class=\"photo\">\r\n		<img alt=\"Val\" border=\"0\" class=\"fr\" id=\"co-founder-img\" src=\"../images/team_2.jpg\" style=\"cursor: default;\" /></div>\r\n	<h5>\r\n		Val Aleksenko<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span>CIO and Co-Founder</span></h5>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Val is responsible for maintaining the BitFatDeals infrastructure, which is proven to handle millions of visitors a day. With over two decades of experience in building and deploying complex systems, Val previously led a team of developers at France Telecom and helped launch Revolution Health. Val studied Computer Science at the Kharkov Polytechnic Institute in Ukraine.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</h4>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>&iquest;Qui&eacute;nes somos en el negocio</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Marketing y Ventas</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	Es el departamento encargado de la b&uacute;squeda de las mejores opciones para nuestras ofertas. Es el responsable de que dailydeals una experiencia agradable para miembros y afiliados.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	Desarrollo y TI</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	Cada d&iacute;a este departamento tiene la ardua tarea de dailydeals.fatbit.com experimentar lo mejor en tu ordenador, tableta o tel&eacute;fono m&oacute;vil.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Cliente</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	Si se trata de una sugerencia, queja, o una simple pregunta, servicio al cliente est&aacute; siempre dispuesto a ayudarle en cualquier momento.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Imagen y Publicidad</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	La imagen es muy importante si queremos disfrutar de la ciudad. Este departamento no s&oacute;lo asegura que dailydeals tienen buena presentaci&oacute;n, pero para crear una experiencia visual ya que las compras de ofertas hasta que disfrutes con tus amigos.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Cuentas</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	El departamento de Cuentas se refiere all&aacute; dailydeals llevan un simple negocios. Asegura que crecen marcas, ofreciendo nuevas experiencias a nuestros afiliados y afiliadas.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<strong>Prensa</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	Siempre hay algo interesante que hacer y el Departamento de Prensa es el encargado de hacer que se obtiene lo mejor de la revisi&oacute;n de temas como la alimentaci&oacute;n, los viajes, la tecnolog&iacute;a, el arte, la moda, la salud y las tendencias, por nombrar algunos.</p>', 0, 2, 2, 0),
