(19, '<section class=\"page__container\">\r\n	<div class=\"fixed_container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n				<div class=\"content__centered\">\r\n					<h3>\r\n						How it Works</h3>\r\n					<h6>\r\n						Like today&#39;s deal? Simply click on the Buy button, choose your method of payment<br />\r\n						and wait for your voucher to be emailed to you within 24 hours</h6>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<ul class=\"timeline\">\r\n					<li>\r\n						<div class=\"timeline__content\">\r\n							<span class=\"counter\">1</span>\r\n							<div class=\"timeline__content-cell\">\r\n								<figure class=\"cell--icon\">\r\n									<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_1.svg\" /></figure>\r\n								<div class=\"cell--text\">\r\n									<h4>\r\n										What&#39;s the Big Deal?</h4>\r\n									<p>\r\n										<strong>Yo!Deals </strong> offers one fantastic deal every day with discounts of up to 90% at local restaurants, bars, spas, heaters, and more.</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<div class=\"timeline__content\">\r\n							<span class=\"counter\">2</span>\r\n							<div class=\"timeline__content-cell\">\r\n								<figure class=\"cell--icon\">\r\n									<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_2.svg\" /></figure>\r\n								<div class=\"cell--text\">\r\n									<h4>\r\n										Spam-Free</h4>\r\n									<p>\r\n										Gift Cards can be printed out and delivered to your loved ones or friends in-person or shared over email. Our Gift Cards consist of a simple code that can be applied to your purchase when you check-out.</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<div class=\"timeline__content\">\r\n							<span class=\"counter\">3</span>\r\n							<div class=\"timeline__content-cell\">\r\n								<figure class=\"cell--icon\">\r\n									<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_3.svg\" /></figure>\r\n								<div class=\"cell--text\">\r\n									<h4>\r\n										Quality Merchants</h4>\r\n									<p>\r\n										Just select the amount and how many you&rsquo;d like to purchase and you&rsquo;re on your way. We have a price for every budget!</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<div class=\"timeline__content\">\r\n							<span class=\"counter\">4</span>\r\n							<div class=\"timeline__content-cell\">\r\n								<figure class=\"cell--icon\">\r\n									<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_4.svg\" /></figure>\r\n								<div class=\"cell--text\">\r\n									<h4>\r\n										Clear, Simple Terms</h4>\r\n									<p>\r\n										Once you selected your amount, just hit Add to Cart and it will automatically be placed in your cart. You can purchase as many gift cards as you want. Once you&rsquo;re ready to complete your order, click Shopping Cart at the top of the page to review and finish your purchase.</p>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</li>\r\n				</ul>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>', '<div class=\"innerbanner\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/innerbanner.jpg\" style=\"cursor: default;\" />\r\n	<div class=\"contentWrap\">\r\n		&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"content_container\" style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">\r\n	<h3 class=\"pageTitle\">\r\n		<span>C&oacute;mo funciona</span></h3>\r\n	<h4>\r\n		&nbsp;</h4>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Al igual que la oferta de hoy ? Simplemente haga clic en el bot&oacute;n Comprar , elegir la forma de pago y esperar su confirmaci&oacute;n a ser enviado por correo electr&oacute;nico dentro de 24 horas</p>\r\n	<div class=\"workinfo\">\r\n		<div class=\"block\">\r\n			<span class=\"iconblock\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_1.png\" style=\"cursor: default;\" /></span>\r\n			<h5>\r\n				Cu&aacute;l es el problema?</h5>\r\n			<p>\r\n				BitFatDeals ofrece una fant&aacute;stica oferta todos los d&iacute;as con descuentos de hasta el 90 % en los restaurantes locales , bares , spas, calentadores, y mucho m&aacute;s.</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\">\r\n			<span class=\"iconblock\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_3.png\" style=\"cursor: default;\" /></span>\r\n			<h5>\r\n				Los comerciantes de Calidad</h5>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				S&oacute;lo tienes que seleccionar la cantidad y cu&aacute;ntos y rsquo ; d tiene gusto de comprar y usted y rsquo; re en su camino . Nosotros tenemos precios para todos los bolsillos !</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"workinfo last\">\r\n		<div class=\"block\">\r\n			<span class=\"iconblock\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_2.png\" style=\"cursor: default;\" /></span>\r\n			<h5>\r\n				Libre de spam</h5>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				Tarjetas de regalo puede ser impreso y entregado a sus seres queridos o amigos en persona o compartir a trav&eacute;s de correo electr&oacute;nico. Nuestra Tarjetas de regalo consiste en un c&oacute;digo simple que se puede aplicar a su compra cuando el registro de salida.</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"block\">\r\n			<span class=\"iconblock\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/hw_icon_4.png\" style=\"cursor: default;\" /></span>\r\n			<h5>\r\n				T&eacute;rminos claros y sencillos</h5>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				Una vez que haya seleccionado su importe , simplemente pulse A&ntilde;adir a la cesta y se colocar&aacute; autom&aacute;ticamente en su cesta . Usted puede comprar tantas tarjetas de regalo como desee. Una vez que usted y rsquo; re listo para completar su pedido , haga clic en Cesta de la compra en la parte superior de la p&aacute;gina para revisar y terminar su compra.</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				&nbsp;</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<h3 class=\"pageTitle\">\r\n		<span>La Oferta del D&iacute;a</span></h3>\r\n	<ul class=\"titleList\" style=\"padding: 0px 40px;\">\r\n		<li>\r\n			<h5>\r\n				Grandes ofertas</h5>\r\n			<h6>\r\n				Hasta un 90 % de descuento en la mejor de tu ciudad.</h6>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li class=\"last\">\r\n			<h5>\r\n				Los comerciantes de Calidad</h5>\r\n			<h6>\r\n				Seleccionados para ti por nuestros expertos en el terreno.</h6>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n			<h5>\r\n				Terminos claros y sencillos</h5>\r\n			<h6>\r\n				No digo mas.</h6>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li class=\"last\">\r\n			<h5>\r\n				Libre de spam</h5>\r\n			<h6>\r\n				Usted firm&oacute; para ofertas de calidad y eso es lo que vamos a traer.</h6>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', 0, 17, 2, 0),
